<input type="text" id="module4_tf_q8" name="module4_tf_q8" maxlength="1" placeholder="T or F" style="width: 55px;" data-correct-answer="F" /> 
<label for="module4_tf_q8"><strong>Beta corresponds to the slope of the best fitting line in the plot of a security‚Äôs excess returns versus the market‚Äôs standard deviation.</strong></label>
